# 🚀 Responsive Landing Page A sleek and fully responsive landing page built with **HTML5**, **CSS3**, and **JavaScript**. Perfect for showcasing your product, service, or personal brand — works seamlessly across mobile, tablet, and desktop. --- ## 📸 Demo ![Landing Page Screenshot](demo-image.png) *(Replace `demo-image.png` with your screenshot or live demo link)* 🔗 **Live Demo:** [View here](https://your-demo-link.com) --- ## ✨ Features - **Responsive Design** – Looks great on all devices. - **Fixed Navigation Bar** – Always visible while scrolling. - **Hamburger Menu** – Collapsible navigation for mobile. - **Hero Section** – Eye-catching intro with a call-to-action. - **Feature Grid** – Showcase your services or product highlights. - **Clean Typography & Hover Effects** – Modern user experience. --- ## 🛠️ Technologies Used - **HTML5** – For semantic structure. - **CSS3 (Flexbox & Grid)** – For responsive layouts and styling. - **JavaScript (Vanilla)** – For navbar interactivity. - **Media Queries** – For device-specific design adjustments. --- ## 🎨 Color Palette | Element | Color Code | |----------------------|------------| | Primary Gradient Start | `#FF9800` | | Primary Gradient End | `#FF5722` | | Navbar & Footer BG | `#222222` | | Text Color | `#FFFFFF` | | Button Hover BG | `#FFCCBC` | | Section BG (Features) | `#F4F4F4` | --- ## 🚀 Getting Started ### 1️⃣ Prerequisites - Any code editor (**VS Code** recommended) - Web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge) ### 2️⃣ Installation ```bash # Clone the repository git clone https://github.com/your-username/landing-page.git # Navigate into the project folder cd landing-page 
