🤝 Contributing
We welcome contributions! To get started:
• Fork the repository.
• Clone your fork: git clone https://github.com/your-username/landing-page.git 
• Create a new branch: git checkout -b feature/your-feature 
• Make changes and test them.
• Commit your changes: git commit -m "Add: short description" 
• Push to your branch: git push origin feature/your-feature 
• Open a Pull Request on GitHub.
Guidelines:
• Keep commits small and clear.
• Follow the existing color palette and style.
• Test on mobile and desktop before submitting.
